creator: Scrapo, Inc
descriptionHtml:
Scrapo is the largest marketplace for trading recycling plastics worldwide.

Our marketplace benefits sellers because it allows you to connect directly with buyers from around the world to find out exactly how much your materials are worth and negotiate a deal on the go. Creating a new listing can be done from your phone in less than a minute.

Buyers benefit because you have immediate access to every listing on the platform, and you can directly negotiate with sellers to determine a fair price for any listing you may be interested in. Negotiations happen in real-time, so no more emails or waiting for seller's response.

Whether you buy, sell, or do a little of both, you’ll benefit from using an open market to list and source materials.

Start using Scrapo today to trade directly with suppliers and buyers of recyclable plastics.


Upgrade to Premium

Upgrade to Premium   to have unlimited chats with suppliers of quality material, have access to verified sellers, post unlimited number of offers, bump up your offers to the top of the Home page, and have premium tag in your profile and messages.

Subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period.

Premium subscription price is $19.99/Month. Prices are in the U.S. dollars, may vary in countries other than the U.S. and are subject to change without notice. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.
descriptionShort: The easiest and fastest way to buy and sell recyclable plastics globally
